cuems-wsclient (0.2.3-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Ship debian/cuems-power-bridge.service from this package instead of
    cuems-common. The unit belongs with the .deb that actually runs the
    daemon — cuems-power-bridge is an opt-in controller-only install,
    whereas cuems-common lands on every CUEMS host. Picked up
    automatically by dh_installsystemd. The companion sudoers file stays
    in cuems-common (every host needs the NOPASSWD entry so the bridge's
    SSH-fanout poweroff lands on nodes that don't have this package).

